                        <accMat>
                            <p xml:id="accMat1">One sheet of paper inserted at the front of the manuscript, bearing a large round stamp with the
                                caption: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማህተመ፡ ዘባራባራስ፡ ተስፋ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign> and the following texts:
                                <foreign xml:lang="am">መልእክት፡ ዘ<persName ref="PRS15358TasfaMar" role="owner"><roleName type="title">
                                    ባራምባራስ፡</roleName> ተስፋ፡ ማርያም፡</persName> ይደ<add place="above">ረ</add>ስ፡ ኃበ፡ አቡየ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ወንጹሕ፡ አቃቢሃ፡
                                    ለጽዮን፡ መምህር፡ <persName ref="PRS15359TaklaHaym" role="owner">ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName> እንዴት፡ እሉ፡ እጅጉን፡
                                    እኔ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ይመስገን፡ ደህና፡ ነኝ፡ 
                                    <persName ref="PRS15360GabraIyas"><roleName type="title">ደብተራ፡</roleName> ገብረ፡ ኢየሱስ</persName>ና፡ 
                                    <persName ref="PRS15361GabraEgz"><roleName type="title">መምሬ፡</roleName> ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</persName>
                                    <sic>ገዘህኝ፡</sic> <sic>ተሎ፡</sic> ብለው፡ እንዲ፡ <sic>ስዱሉኝ፡</sic> ይሁን፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ላሰራ፡ ብየ፡</foreign> and
                                <foreign xml:lang="am">ይደረስ፡ ከ<persName ref="PRS15359TaklaHaym" role="owner">
                                    <roleName type="title">መምህር፡</roleName> ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName></foreign>.</p></accMat>
                        
