                                <msItem xml:id="p1_i1.1">
                                    <locus from="4ra" to="28r"/>
                                    <title>Homilies of the Archangel Gabriel for Tāhsās 22 and 19</title>
                                    <note>Indicated with <foreign xml:lang="gez">አመ፡ ፳፪ ለታሕሣሥ፡</foreign> and 
                                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">አመ፡ ፲ወ፱ ለታሕሣሥ፡</foreign> on <locus target="#4r"/> and 
                                        <locus target="24ra"/>.</note>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p1_i1.1.1">
                                        <locus from="4ra" to="24ra"/>
                                        <title ref="LIT7718HomilyGab"/>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ፍሡሐ፡ ገጽ፡ እምእለ፡ 
                                            ይተግሁ፡ መላእክት፡ አብሳሬ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ወኃሤት።</incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p1_i1.1.2">
                                        <locus from="24ra" to="28rb"/>
                                        <title ref="LIT7807TahsasMir"/>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡ አመ፡
                                            <add place="above">፲ወ፱፡ ለታሕሣሥ፡</add> በዓሉ፡ ዘይትነበብ። <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ሠምረ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
                                            ከመ፡ እሑር፡ ኀበ፡ አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡ ቅዱሳት፡ ዘሐነጸቶን፡ እሌኒ፡ ንግሥት፡ ኀበ፡ ቅድስት፡ ሀገረ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፤</incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                </msItem>
                                <msItem xml:id="p1_i1.2">
