                                <note>Fragment of an unidentified text, possibly <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2296Sayfas"/>.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> በቅድስት፡ ሠላሴ፡ እንዘ፡ አአምን፡ ዘእትመሐፀን፡ 
